---
title: Chicken in a Velvety Mushroom Sauce with Bacon, Bistro Salad & Garlic Bread
description: Get ready to be transported to a wine country inn when you tuck in to this chic yet simple dinner. Seared chicken is topped with a lush mushroom sauce that’s perked up with red wine vinegar for beautiful balance. On the side, a crisp green salad topped with smoky bacon and grapes offering pops of freshness, plus there’s garlic bread to scoop up that dreamy sauce.
